### ============================================================
### PREREQUISITES — Auth + Classroom
### Chạy file này trước, theo đúng thứ tự từ trên xuống.
### Copy token/ID từ response vào http-client.env.json
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### [1] Đăng ký tài khoản TEACHER
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Giáo viên Test",
  "email": "teacher@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "TEACHER"
}

### [2] Đăng nhập TEACHER — copy data.accessToken → teacherToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### [3] Đăng ký STUDENT 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Học sinh 1",
  "email": "student1@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### [4] Đăng nhập STUDENT 1 — copy data.accessToken → student1Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### [5] Đăng ký STUDENT 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Học sinh 2",
  "email": "student2@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### [6] Đăng nhập STUDENT 2 — copy data.accessToken → student2Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student2@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### [7] Teacher tạo lớp học — copy data.id → classroomId
# Thay <TEACHER_TOKEN> bằng token thực
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMTExMTc0Zi1jN2ViLTQwMDctYjRjMC1kZDRkNTkxOTU3YTMiLCJyb2xlIjoidGVhY2hlciIsIm5hbWUiOiJHacOhbyB2acOqbiBUZXN0IiwianRpIjoiZDViOTA0MmQtN2U0Ni00YjAxLWI3NTItOWFlNDg2M2IwODk0IiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4MzA4NDI1LCJleHAiOjE3NzgzMDkzMjV9.kaqd7NfdZy7taXuko_lAaXvpbbyNt789gEaOId8DBV2kY-ENk0YdofM4HZD2QTnQBxfBUGZ7YLhBv3iuff3_4w

{
  "name": "Lớp Test M09-M11",
  "description": "Lớp để test Session, Question, Answer"
}

